org.forgerock.openam.authentication.service.protocol

Class RemoteServletRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.authentication.service.protocol.RemoteServletRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, javax.servlet.ServletRequest
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RemoteHttpServletRequest

    public class RemoteServletRequest
extends Object
implements javax.servlet.ServletRequest, Serializable
    This class encapsulates a ServletRequest allowing its state to be serialized.
